Dim FileName as string
FileName = "diag_en_help"
If (Trim(FileName) == "") Then Exit Sub End If If !PRJSPEC.IE_Exists(FileName, False) Then ShowError("Не найден файл\n" + FileName + ".htm", 0) Exit Sub Else FileName = FileName + ".htm" 'Грузим в новое окно Dim Path_and_Name As String Path_and_Name = VAR("VIS.PORTAL_ROOT").ValueString() + VAR("VIS.IE_ROOT_PATH").ValueString() + FileName
VIS.CreateWindowEx("IEWindow", "Default", "", FileName, 1100, 700, 0, 0, Path_and_Name, "") VIS.Window(FileName).Title = "Инструкция по восстановлению "+FileName
End If
